title: Meeting House Cafe
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Organic, Take-out, British, English
description: Liverpool Quakers teamed with Blackburne House Cafe to open this eatery in late-July 2014. It's situated inside the Liverpool Quaker Meeting House. Offers seasonal food like granola and porridge, soup and fresh bread, sandwiches and paninis, baked potatoes, quiche, and salads.
